{"tid":644250,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"小童星激似IU引起熱議，她還有「韓國最美女童」的稱號～","createTime":"2018-04-27T06:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T11:51:14.000Z","uid":34643,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"14bb3394d17bcebe3e7b46405f89596b56c3ad70","tid":644250,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:26:38.000Z","msg":"《我的大叔》劇情進入高潮，飾演知安小時候的這一位童星，即使一句話都沒說，但卻讓人「超入戲」，因為小童星的樣貌和IU小時候簡直是「複製貼上」，加上她和劇中知安有著一樣的造型，暗色系衣服和凌亂髮型，讓人對小童星印象好深刻，劇組這個選角真的太用心、太厲害啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://kdaily-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/1704.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkdaily-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F1704.jpg&h=734d13ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實這位小童星早就因為撞臉IU而很有知名度，她叫做金奎莉（音譯，韓文名김규리），2008年出生，今年剛滿10歲，是一位很有名氣的兒童模特兒。右圖為IU小時候，放在一起比較，是不是很相像呢？金奎莉甚至還被譽為「韓國最美女童」，她拍攝過許多廣告及服飾形象照，有著超齡的氣質，不論是可愛打扮還是成熟造型，都讓人感嘆基因太強大，完全天生麗質啊～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://kdaily-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/1710.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkdaily-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F1710.jpg&h=e07c0955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://kdaily-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/1711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkdaily-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F1711.jpg&h=2cd609cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金奎莉有一雙圓圓的大眼睛，以及精緻小巧的嘴巴和鼻子，大家是不是也覺得和IU真的有幾分相像呢？小小年紀就有著如此出眾的美貌，加上現在還漸漸地朝戲劇發展，不知道未來會不會有更多機會在電視上看到金奎莉的身影？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://kdaily-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/1707.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkdaily-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F1707.jpg&h=fdc2140f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《我的大叔》的拍攝真的很用心，雖然劇情很貼近現實很沉重，但總能讓人在其中得到治癒和幸福，希望最後知安和大叔都能獲得幸福，大家也要持續鎖定每週三、四晚上《我的大叔》的播出喔！"},{"pid":"45107b36807a70aa8694a359ec30bac36c651a18","tid":644250,"uid":114292,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"邊到似"},{"pid":"abbba8e38d7031c586e48090f0b99b0127cafd62","tid":644250,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:28:08.000Z","msg":"差好遠喎<br />\n成個支那農民咁"},{"pid":"dde1d04edb4f901fe36fd45c8dd5e760b523a5ab","tid":644250,"uid":18568,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"abbba8e38d7031c586e48090f0b99b0127cafd62","tid":644250,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:28:08.000Z","msg":"差好遠喎<br />\n成個支那農民咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:30:30.000Z","msg":"咁都似支那農民<br />\nChing 住係邊到<br />\n咁多靚女"},{"pid":"a8596238b943119f49bc25d8bb828d00449d7305","tid":644250,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45107b36807a70aa8694a359ec30bac36c651a18","tid":644250,"uid":114292,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"邊到似"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:34:57.000Z","msg":"最唔似係個咀, iu個咀形靚好多"},{"pid":"d91f4139d6e86aa3c3d2ea1e3d44f8002556d48f","tid":644250,"uid":37146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"激你老母似咩<br />\nIU個鼻已經唔係靚，條𡃁妹個鼻仲要仲柒"},{"pid":"85feeceda2c13e9ab94988fec9c265f05bfc3e4e","tid":644250,"uid":72076,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T11:51:14.000Z","msg":"臉蛋似 完"}]}